Lady Hawk approaches the lab. "This will do for the time. I'll set up my
specimen samples and give you a suitable demonstration. It may be to
difficult for a bot with limited scientific programming to understand." she
says as she steps into the lab, "As for Battera, I need not an army so I
worry not about her."

After a short scan of the lab Lady Hawk steps back and sees the activity
(Zardus and Feline trying to switch processors in Squizzy.) "Interesting
technique, I've never seen anyone trying so hard to fail before, what
exactly are you trying to do?"
